Brad Pitt has reportedly spent some quality time with all six of his kids, who he shares with former wife Angelina Jolie, at his house in Los Feliz, California.The 53-year-old actor has been in custody battle with Jolie over their kids after the pair announced separation last September.His kids visited him at his Los Feliz home on the evening of April 2.According to the source, it was the first time since the actor separated from Jolie that all of their six kids were with him at one time.This article first appeared on Times of India 